ck py-2.5 px-3 font-exo font-semibold text-[0.8rem] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-navy/75 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/services/marketing\">Online Marketing</a></li></ul></div></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/pricing\">Pricing</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/scorecard\">Scorecard</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/faq\">FAQ</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></li><li class=\"py-4\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary w-full justify-center\" href=\"/contact\">Get Started <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a></li></ul></div></header><main class=\"font-rajdhani\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"LocalBusiness\",\"name\":\"Tech 4 Underdogs\",\"description\":\"IT support, web design, and local marketing built for small businesses.\",\"url\":\"https://tech4underdogs.com/contact\",\"email\":\"contact@tech4underdogs.com\",\"areaServed\":\"United States\"}</script><section class=\"bg-cream overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"section-container section-y\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr] gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center\"><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><p class=\"eyebrow mb-5\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>Contact Tech 4 Underdogs</p><h1 class=\"h-section text-navy mb-6 text-balance\" style=\"font-size:clamp(2.2rem, 4.6vw, 4.25rem)\">Tell us what&#x27;s<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-orange whitespace-nowrap\">going on.</span> <!-- -->We&#x27;ll<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-outlined-navy whitespace-nowrap\">take it from there.</span></h1><div class=\"lg:hidden flex justify-center mb-8\"><img alt=\"Archie the Tech 4 Underdogs mascot, ready to help\" width=\"560\" height=\"620\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full max-w-[280px] sm:max-w-[340px] h-auto object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-On-Your-Side.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-On-Your-Side.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-On-Your-Side.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75\"/></div><p class=\"body-text lg:max-w-[480px] mb-9 text-[1.05rem]\">IT support, a new website, or help getting found online — start here. Tell us a little about your business and what you&#x27;re dealing with. We respond within one business day. No pressure, no pitch.</p><p class=\"tagline text-navy\">Steady. Reliable.<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-orange\">On your side.</span></p></div><div class=\"hidden lg:flex justify-end\"><img alt=\"Archie the Tech 4 Underdogs mascot, ready to help\" width=\"620\" height=\"620\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full max-w-[490px] xl:max-w-[550px] h-auto object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-On-Your-Side.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-On-Your-Side.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-On-Your-Side.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"/></div></div></div></section><section id=\"form\" class=\"scroll-mt-20 overflow-hidden bg-teal-gradient\"><div class=\"section-container section-y\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1.2fr] gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start\"><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><p class=\"eyebrow eyebrow-dark mb-5\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>Let&#x27;s talk</p><h2 class=\"h-section mb-6 text-balance\"><span class=\"text-white\">No commitment. </span><span class=\"italic text-white\">No pitch.</span><br/><span class=\"text-white\">Just a </span><span class=\"italic text-orange\">real conversation.</span></h2><p class=\"body-text body-text-dark max-w-[480px] mb-9 text-pretty\">A straightforward talk about your technology, your website, or your marketing — and whether we&#x27;re the right fit to help.</p><ul class=\"space-y-3 mb-8\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-white/80 font-exo font-medium text-[0.95rem]\"><span class=\"text-orange mt-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span>Response within one business day</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-white/80 font-exo font-medium text-[0.95rem]\"><span class=\"text-orange mt-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span>Talk to a real person, not a script</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-white/80 font-exo font-medium text-[0.95rem]\"><span class=\"text-orange mt-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span>No sales pressure, ever</li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 sm:p-9 shadow-xl\"><form noValidate=\"\" class=\"flex flex-col gap-5\"><div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5\"><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><label for=\"firstName\" class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy/70 mb-2\">First name<span class=\"text-orange ml-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">*</span></label><input id=\"firstName\" type=\"text\" autoComplete=\"given-name\" class=\"font-exo font-medium text-[0.95rem] text-navy bg-cream/60 border rounded-md px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 transition-colors border-navy/15 focus:border-orange focus:ring-orange/30\" name=\"firstName\"/></div><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><label for=\"businessName\" class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy/70 mb-2\">Business name<span class=\"text-orange ml-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">*</span></label><input id=\"businessName\" type=\"text\" autoComplete=\"organization\" class=\"font-exo font-medium text-[0.95rem] text-navy bg-cream/60 border rounded-md px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 transition-colors border-navy/15 focus:border-orange focus:ring-orange/30\" name=\"businessName\"/></div></div><div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5\"><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><label for=\"email\" class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy/70 mb-2\">Email<span class=\"text-orange ml-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">*</span></label><input id=\"email\" type=\"email\" autoComplete=\"email\" class=\"font-exo font-medium text-[0.95rem] text-navy bg-cream/60 border rounded-md px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 transition-colors border-navy/15 focus:border-orange focus:ring-orange/30\" name=\"email\"/></div><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><label for=\"phone\" class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy/70 mb-2\">Phone<span class=\"font-medium text-navy/40 normal-case tracking-normal ml-1\">(optional)</span></label><input id=\"phone\" type=\"tel\" autoComplete=\"tel\" class=\"font-exo font-medium text-[0.95rem] text-navy bg-cream/60 border rounded-md px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 transition-colors border-navy/15 focus:border-orange focus:ring-orange/30\" name=\"phone\"/></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><label for=\"service\" class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy/70 mb-2\">What do you need help with?</label><select id=\"service\" name=\"service\" class=\"font-exo font-medium text-[0.95rem] text-navy bg-cream/60 border border-navy/15 rounded-md px-4 py-3 focus:border-orange focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-orange/30 transition-colors cursor-pointer\"><option value=\"it-support\">IT Support &amp; Security</option><option value=\"web-design\">Web Design &amp; Hosting</option><option value=\"marketing\">Online Marketing</option><option value=\"not-sure\" selected=\"\">Not sure yet</option></select></div><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><label for=\"message\" class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy/70 mb-2\">What&#x27;s going on? <span class=\"font